{"tid":4792,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老爸誤傳挑逗裸照給女兒 網民已分享百萬次","createTime":"2016-11-26T15:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T18:36:14.000Z","uid":12709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e5ecc75f64a4766b6229c0fa60e2bb46469212","tid":4792,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"英國一名18歲少女米倫(Robyn Millen)日前在手機上收到一張照片，打開一看發現竟然是老爸的挑逗裸照。老爸事後表示是誤傳，還直呼「很想死」。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這位老爸寄了一張裸露下半身、泡在浴缸的照片，不過重點部位已經用多個表情符號遮住，而照片上的文字寫著：「情人節快樂。」米倫收到後，馬上回信給老爸：「爸，你在Snapchat上寄來的照片很不妥喔！」這位老爸隨即發現自己誤傳照片給女兒，他本來是打算傳給老婆調情的，之後他也向女兒道歉，表示自己對Snapchat的操作不熟悉，才導致「悲劇」發生。<br />\n <br />\n米倫之後把這張照片和故事上傳推特，就引來150萬次的轉發率。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160218/640_11202b652d40db29b046e5d722f53f9f.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160218%2F640_11202b652d40db29b046e5d722f53f9f.jpg&d=KAbvVb99HXKgOeR6UCIXGMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f9e2d7cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160218/640_11202b652d40db29b046e5d722f53f9f.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"f6016060a57c70395d10284f18dac15a1d959d92","tid":4792,"uid":6076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:53:28.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419e454d02f8d4bfb6fb5367d2836c657b5b6eca","tid":4792,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092172a7e5d260e5fb26d806e3ff2175892b4c21","tid":4792,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"有心扮無意😏"},{"pid":"56b5abdc9021d685d150aea8